            "effect": "The Gorumite infantry engages in a frenzied attack against each enemy within 10 feet, with a DC 31 basic Reflex save. The damage depends on the number of actions.  \n [#] 1d12+4 slashing damage.  \n [##] 2d12+10 slashing damage and 1d6 persistent bleed damage.  \n [###] 3d12+10 slashing damage and 2d6 persistent bleed damage.",
